trans-unit.source: Contains a collection of <see cref="T:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution" /> objects.
trans-unit.target: Contém uma coleção de objetos <see cref="T:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution" /> .

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.PrinterResolutionCollection> contains <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution> instances that represents the printer resolutions supported through the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property, which contains one of the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind> values.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.PrinterResolutionCollection> contém <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution> instâncias que representa as resoluções de impressora têm suportadas por meio de <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> propriedade, que contém uma da <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind> valores.

trans-unit.source: Typically, you set the printer's resolution through the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings.PrinterResolution%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property to a valid <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution> instance available through the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.PrinterResolutions%2A> collection.
trans-unit.target: Normalmente, você pode definir a resolução da impressora por meio de <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings.PrinterResolution%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> propriedade válido <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution> disponíveis por meio da instância a <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.PrinterResolutions%2A> coleção.

trans-unit.source: If <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind> is `Custom`, then use the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.X%2A> and <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Y%2A> properties to determine the custom printer resolution in the horizontal and vertical directions, respectively.
trans-unit.target: Se <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind> é `Custom`, em seguida, use o <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.X%2A> e <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Y%2A> propriedades para determinar a resolução de impressão personalizada nas direções horizontais e verticais, respectivamente.

trans-unit.source: The following code example populates the `comboPrintResolution` combo box with the supported resolutions.
trans-unit.target: O exemplo de código a seguir preenche a `comboPrintResolution` caixa de combinação com as resoluções com suporte.

trans-unit.source: The example requires that a <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument> variable named `printDoc` exists and that the specific combo box exists.
trans-unit.target: O exemplo requer que um <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument> variável chamada `printDoc` existe e se a caixa de combinação específico existe.

trans-unit.source: This method instantiates an enumerator that takes a snapshot of the current state of the collection.
trans-unit.target: Esse método cria um enumerador que tira um instantâneo do estado atual da coleção.

trans-unit.source: The enumerator does not have exclusive access to the collection, so multiple enumerators can have access to the same collection at the same time.
trans-unit.target: O enumerador não tem acesso exclusivo à coleção, para que vários enumeradores podem ter acesso à mesma coleção ao mesmo tempo.

trans-unit.source: Therefore, any changes made to the collection, either directly or through another enumerator, can cause <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A> or <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> to throw an exception.
trans-unit.target: Portanto, quaisquer alterações feitas à coleção, diretamente ou através de outro enumerador podem causar <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A> ou <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> para lançar uma exceção.

trans-unit.source: Two enumerators instantiated from the same collection at the same time can contain different snapshots of the collection.
trans-unit.target: Dois enumeradores criadas a partir do mesmo conjunto ao mesmo tempo podem conter diferentes instantâneos da coleção.

trans-unit.source: Removing objects from the enumerator also removes them from the collection.
trans-unit.target: Removendo objetos do enumerador também remove da coleção.
